Class IdentifiedAnnotation_Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • Annotation_Type
      • org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.textsem.IdentifiedAnnotation_Type
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContextAnnotation_Type, DateAnnotation_Type, EntityMention_Type, EventMention_Type, FractionAnnotation_Type, Markable_Type, MeasurementAnnotation_Type, Modifier_Type, NonSmokerNamedEntityAnnotation_Type, PersonTitleAnnotation_Type, RangeAnnotation_Type, RomanNumeralAnnotation_Type, SmokerNamedEntityAnnotation_Type, TimeAnnotation_Type, TimeMention_Type, UnknownSmokerNamedEntityAnnotation_Type

    public class IdentifiedAnnotation_Type
extends Annotation_Type
    Any span of text that has been discovered or flagged for some reason, such as a Named Entity. Allows for mapping to an ontology. Generalized from cTAKES: org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.IdentifiedAnnotation. Updated by JCasGen Wed Sep 30 11:06:15 EDT 2015
